  <brief_title>Effects of Antimicrobial Photodynamic Therapy on Regeneration of Class II Furcation Lesions</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Antimicrobial Photodynamic Therapy Associated to Biomaterials on Regeneration of Class II Furcation Lesions</official_title>
