  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the additional effect of antimicrobial photodynamic
      therapy regeneration treatment of mandibular furcation lesions when associated to bovine bone
      and porcine collagen membrane.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
